OL,3,CScottish parliament announces #500
OL,4,Cmillion spending cuts
OL,6,FScotland's Finance Secretary has
OL,7,Fannounced cuts to green policies, as
OL,8,Fpart of half a billion pounds worth of
OL,9,Fsavings the government is trying to
OL,10,Fmake, our Scotland Correspondent Peter
OL,11,FSmith reports
OL,13,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,14,FGlenton
OL,16,FThe Scottish finance minister has
OL,17,Fannounced severe cuts to the country's
OL,18,Fpublic services, saying the current
OL,19,Ffinancial situation is "not
OL,20,Fsustainable".
