OL,3,CScottish parliament announces #500
OL,4,Cmillion spending cuts
OL,6,FShona Robison announced up to #500
OL,7,Fmillion worth of cuts, including #188
OL,8,Fmillion to be found across government
OL,9,Fdepartments, saying: "I must take
OL,10,Ffurther and more urgent action now to
OL,11,Fmake sure we can balance the Scottish
OL,12,Fbudget."
OL,14,FThat included #115.8 million of
OL,15,Fsavings from the health and social
OL,16,Fcare budget, but in a letter to MSPs
OL,17,Fon Holyrood's Finance Committee,
OL,18,FRobison offered "assurances that the
OL,19,Fhealth portfolio will seek to protect
OL,20,Fkey frontline emergency services".
