OL,3,CScottish parliament announces #500
OL,4,Cmillion spending cuts
OL,6,FThe government also plans to cut
OL,7,Factive travel funding and repurpose
OL,8,Fmoney from other projects to save #65
OL,9,Fmillion, on top of around #60 million
OL,10,Fsaved through spending controls
OL,11,Falready announced.
OL,13,FRobison said that on top of the
OL,14,F"direct savings" she would make, up to
OL,15,F#460 million from the ScotWind leasing
OL,16,Fround - the process by which Scotland
OL,17,Fleases its seabed to companies wanting
OL,18,Fto build offshore wind farms - will
OL,19,Falso be used, but with the hope it
OL,20,Fwouldn't all need to be spent.
