OL,3,CScottish parliament announces #500
OL,4,Cmillion spending cuts
OL,6,F"It is not what I would want to be
OL,7,Fdoing," Robison said when questioned
OL,8,Fon why ScotWind funds were being
OL,9,Futilised.
OL,11,FRobison did not outline any changes to
OL,12,Ftaxation, but hinted that the Scottish
OL,13,Fgovernment would not increase income
OL,14,Ftax at the next Scottish Budget.
OL,16,FShe highlighted that raising
OL,17,Fsignificant funds from additional
OL,18,Ftaxation would be challenging because
OL,19,Fit would involved "substantial reform"
OL,20,Fto the tax system or further
OL,21,Fdevolution of powers.
