OL,6,FA number of measures had already been
OL,7,Fannounced, including the government
OL,8,Fredirecting money from a nature fund
OL,9,Fand a free iPad scheme to go towards
OL,10,Flocal authority pay awards.
OL,12,FOpposition parties have blamed the
OL,13,Ffinancial shortfalls on the SNP's
OL,14,Fprevious spending plans.
