OL,3,CScottish parliament announces #500
OL,4,Cmillion spending cuts
OL,6,FAhead of her statement statement, Ms
OL,7,FRobison said: "The SNP Government has
OL,8,Fdelivered a balanced budget in every
OL,9,Fyear that we have been in office ` and
OL,10,Fwe will continue to do so."
OL,12,F"We have taken many tough choices `
OL,13,Fincluding asking those on higher
OL,14,Fincomes to pay a bit more income tax `
OL,15,Fin order that we can invest more in
OL,16,Fpublic services like our NHS.
