OL,6,F"But the fact is, the Scottish
OL,7,FGovernment operates with a largely
OL,8,Ffixed budget determined by Westminster
OL,9,Fand, under the Labour Government, it
OL,10,Fis clear that we are entering a whole
OL,11,Fnew era of austerity."
OL,13,FFirst Minister John Swinney had
OL,14,Falready warned there are more "tough
OL,15,Fdecisions" ahead, echoing Prime
OL,16,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer, who last
OL,17,Fweek said the October Budget would be
OL,18,F"painful".
